  <brief_title>Cognitive Training in Children With Attention Deficit/ Hyperactivity Disorder (ADHD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study of the Efficacy of Computerized Cognitive Training on Cognitive Function, Symptoms and Functional Outcome in Children With ADHD.</official_title>
  <sponsors>
