  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine the effect of computer program C8 on specific
      cognitive functions, symptoms and functional outcome compared to treatment as usual in
      children with ADHD. Furthermore, if the effect is sustained 12 and 24 weeks after training.
      In addition, it will be investigated, whether younger children benefit more from training
      than older children.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
